An evil industrialist schemes to start world war 3 by wrecking 
the global economy. Bond tracks his foe to a secret Antarctic 
base and they exchange veiled threats. Soon after, Bond meets 
a beautiful KGB agent, whom he seduces. At that moment, Bond 
is betrayed by a triple agent and chained to a bomb. After some 
amazing special effects, he escapes by using his ballpoint pen 
grenade. Finally, with only 007 seconds to spare, Bond restores 
internet service to the world and rides off into the sunset 
with the female interest. 